    <item>
      <title>麦格理称印尼减产可能导致全球镍供应量减少 35%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/indonesia-nickel-move-may-cut-global-supply-35-macquarie-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[麦格理集团有限公司 (Macquarie Group Ltd.) 表示，印尼镍矿产量可能下降，导致全球镍市场供应减少三分之一以上，给镍价带来巨大的上行风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/indonesia-nickel-move-may-cut-global-supply-35-macquarie-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 04:25:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>花旗财富：寻找 2025 年的收益机会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-09/citi-wealth-look-for-yield-opportunities-in-2025-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[花旗财富首席投资策略师 Steven Wieting 表示，固定收益为投资者提供了一个独特的重大机会，可以提高今年从利率到私人信贷的总体回报。他在“彭博：中国秀”节目中与 David Ingles 和 Annabelle Droulers 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-09/citi-wealth-look-for-yield-opportunities-in-2025-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 04:06:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国重点打击金融、能源腐败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-09/china-singles-out-finance-energy-in-anti-graft-fight-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国结束了为期三天的反腐大会，承诺将在金融、能源和体育等多个行业加大反腐力度。反腐行动是国家媒体关注的焦点，中央电视台正在播出有关反腐的纪录片系列。彭博社的 Rebecca Choong Wilkins 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-09/china-singles-out-finance-energy-in-anti-graft-fight-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 03:44:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国如何应对通货紧缩压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-09/what-china-can-do-to-tackle-deflationary-pressures-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国消费者通胀连续第四个月放缓，随着通货紧缩压力持续存在，通胀进一步向零靠拢。法国农业信贷银行首席中国经济学家智晓佳表示，政策制定者需要在 2025 年“采取更多行动”来推动通胀再膨胀。她与 David Ingles 和 Rebecca Choong Wilkins 在“彭博：中国秀”节目中进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-09/what-china-can-do-to-tackle-deflationary-pressures-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 03:30:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国通过创纪录的香港票据发行加大对人民币的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/pboc-taps-record-bill-issuance-in-hong-kong-to-support-yuan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国加大了对陷入困境的人民币的支持，计划在香港市场发行创纪录数量的人民币钞票，以增加海外对人民币的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/pboc-taps-record-bill-issuance-in-hong-kong-to-support-yuan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 01:02:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比看跌押注推动对冲成本升至 2022 年以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/indian-rupee-hedging-costs-highest-since-2022-on-bearish-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着越来越多的人押注印度当局正在放松对卢比的控制，对冲印度资产外汇风险的成本升至两年多来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/indian-rupee-hedging-costs-highest-since-2022-on-bearish-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
